data.description: Assumable loan opportunity with a 4.8% interest rate!! Welcome to 15 Rockridge Road! This charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is a true gem nestled in a desirable tree-lined neighborhood. With a classic brick fireplace, gleaming hardwood floors, and abundant natural light, this home exudes warmth and comfort. Step inside to discover a well-appointed kitchen that opens into a bright dining area, perfect for hosting family and friends. The cozy brick fireplace adds character to the living space, making it ideal for cozy evenings. The highlight of this property is the dual master suites, offering flexibility and privacy. One of these suites features a balcony where you can enjoy picturesque views of the neighborhood. For outdoor enthusiasts, this home is perfect. Explore endless hiking trails, go biking, or indulge in kayaking and boating, all just minutes away. Plus, you're conveniently located a short 5-minute drive from the historical charm of downtown Oroville. An additional perk? The water for this property is sourced from the South Feather River Water Company, keeping water bills at less than $30 a month, ensuring cost-effective living. Don't miss your chance to make 15 Rockridge Drive your new home. It's a perfect blend of comfort, style, and outdoor adventure. Schedule a viewing today!
